*Puno* puta je pokušao da se popravi. (He tried to improve himself many times.)

*Puno* toga se dogodilo u proteklih godinu dana. (A lot happened in the past year.)

*Pun* sam radosti što su svi ok. (I am full of joy that everyone is ok.)

*Punila* se čaša do vrha. (The glass was filled up to the brim.)

*Punio* se autobus za Beograd. (The bus was filling up for Belgrade.)

*Punila* su se sobe u hotelu. (The rooms in the hotel were filling up.)